William Bernstein, money manager and
"The Investor's Manifesto" author, says you cannot pick stocks 
as an individual investor. Bernstein talks with Bloomberg's Tom 
Keene and Michael McKee on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:30
 